title: SebastiAn - A Fine Selection of Remixes (2008)
description:
SebastiAn - A Fine Selection of Remixes
[-------------------------------------]


A Fine Selection of Remixes, a record compiling his SebastiAn's many remixes for Daft Punk, Kelis and the Kills among others. One of the artists that define the unique Ed Banger sound.

Released on Sep 30, 2008.

SebastiAn        : http://www.edbangerrecords.com/site/sebastian/
